<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News]]></title><link/> https://sputniknews.com/新闻<atom:link href="https://rsshub.app/sputniknews" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News - Made with love by RSSHub(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)]]></description><generator> RSSHub</generator><webmaster> i@diygod.me (DIY神)</webmaster><language> zh-cn</language><lastbuilddate> 2023 年 5 月 22 日星期一 01:04:51 GMT</lastbuilddate><ttl> 120 </ttl><item><title><![CDATA[‘Game Changer’ — Huge Network of Ancient Mayan Cities and Highways Could Rewrite History]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110507955" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e4/07/1a/1079986656_0:0:1920:1159_1440x900_80_0_1_25a6112dae6988bd458d3fa489e586b1.jpg?source-sid=cc_0" data-photoview-image-id="1079986654" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/game-changer--huge-network-of-ancient-mayan-cities-and-highways-could-rewrite-history-1110507955.html?share-img=1079986654"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright"><a href="https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/" title="CC0">CC0</a> //</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">库库尔坎古玛雅神庙</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="cc_0" alt="Ancient Mayan Temple of Kukulkan - Sputnik International, 1920, 21.05.2023" title="库库尔坎古玛雅神庙" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e4/07/1a/1079986656_0:40:1920:1120_1920x0_80_0_0_59793cae4f526362a44ad72dafabb93f.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e4/07/1a/1079986656_0:40:1920:1120_640x0_80_0_0_284600adaa2e1b311ea6f81a8a8a5580.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e4/07/1a/1079986656_0:40:1920:1120_1280x0_80_0_0_d10342390137d03ba05ffddafafb1d0f.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e4/07/1a/1079986656_0:40:1920:1120_1920x0_80_0_0_59793cae4f526362a44ad72dafabb93f.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> <a href="https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/" title="CC0">CC0</a> / / </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">悦里德</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_wyatt_reed/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">长期以来，一小群土著研究人员一直在挑战玛雅人是一个相对较新的文明的观念。一项新的研究表明他们一直都是对的。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">科学家们在今天的危地马拉发现了一个由 417 个城市组成的庞大网络，其历史可以追溯到公元前 1000 年左右，这些城市由近 110 英里的“高速公路”相连，这些高速公路被称为“世界上第一个高速公路系统”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">据研究人员称，“激光雷达”技术揭示了一个具有复杂经济、社会和政治体系的高度发达文明的证据——一种相对较新的雷达，用于穿透丛林茂密的树冠和下面的任何灌木丛。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text">除了巨大的道路和城市，许多仪式建筑、农业基础设施，甚至水利系统都表明中美洲古代玛雅文明远比西方学者认为的复杂得多。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110507955" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/game-changer--huge-network-of-ancient-mayan-cities-and-highways-could-rewrite-history-1110507955.html?share-block=1110508224" data-title="In addition to the massive roads and cities, a number of ceremonial buildings, agricultural infrastructure, and even hydraulic systems all suggest Central America’s ancient Mayan civilization was vastly more sophisticated than Western academics have ever given them credit for."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">该研究的主要作者理查德·汉森 (Richard Hansen) <u><a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/science/2023/05/20/mayan-civilization-pyramid-discoveries-guatemala/">表示</a></u>，在这一突破性发现之前，大多数科学家认为，只有该地区的居民才会“游牧成群结队，种植玉米”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “我们现在知道，前古典时期是一个异常复杂和建筑精密的时期，世界历史上一些最大的建筑都是在这段时间建造的，”汉森说，他还领导着一个以玛雅为重点的非营利组织，称为人类学研究基金会和环境研究。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">汉森说，就纠正当权派偏爱的美国历史观点而言，这些发现是“游戏规则的改变者”，并补充说，他们揭开了“我们从未了解的一整卷人类历史”的面纱。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">研究人员说，来自那个时代的文物很可能被后来的玛雅建筑所掩埋，随后被哈勃增长所覆盖。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text">这项<u><a href="https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/ancient-mesoamerica/article/lidar-analyses-in-the-contiguous-miradorcalakmul-karst-basin-guatemala-an-introduction-to-new-perspectives-on-regional-early-maya-socioeconomic-and-political-organization/31075DFA8ADBAA5E7C7320CA6DB93E5E">研究</a></u>被描述为“迄今为止在玛雅低地发表的最大的、连续的、区域性激光雷达研究之一的介绍”，揭示了“超过 775 个古代玛雅定居点……以及周围的 189 个”区域，考古测试发现是从中期和晚期前古典时期。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110507955" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/game-changer--huge-network-of-ancient-mayan-cities-and-highways-could-rewrite-history-1110507955.html?share-block=1110508226" data-title="The study, described as “an introduction to one of the largest, contiguous, regional LiDAR studies published to date in the Maya Lowlands,” revealed “more than 775 ancient Maya settlements… and 189 more in the surrounding” areas, which archeological testing found to be from the Middle and Late Preclassic periods."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">此外，该地区的“纪念性建筑、一致的建筑格式、特定的场地边界、水资源管理/收集设施和 177 公里的高架前古典堤道”表明玛雅人拥有“挑战较小政体组织能力的劳动力投资”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">研究人员说，定居点的数量和分布以及其中建筑的连续性“为特定地理区域内的早期集中管理和社会经济战略提供了证据”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>据报道，该论文的合著者圣卡洛斯大学考古学家恩里克埃尔南德斯表示，这一发现可以与埃及的金字塔相媲美，作为展示古代人类发展的精神象征 - 并且有一天可能会吸引同样多的游客。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">一家美国媒体解释说，特别重要的是“Balamnal 的图像，这是前古典文明的重要中心之一，[which] 首次公开”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">根据主要作者汉森的说法，2009 年之前在 Balamnal 周围进行的挖掘“未能认识到这座城市令人难以置信的复杂程度和规模，所有这些都通过激光雷达技术立即显现出来。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">激光雷达表明该遗址是该地区最大的遗址之一，“辐射到其他较小遗址的道路表明它在前古典时期的行政、经济和政治重要性，”他指出。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 21 May 2023 23:16:16 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/game-changer--huge-network-of-ancient-mayan-cities-and-highways-could-rewrite-history-1110507955.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/game-changer--huge-network-of-ancient-mayan-cities-and-highways-could-rewrite-history-1110507955.html<category>超越政治</category><category>玛雅人</category><category>历史</category><category>古代历史</category><category>科学与技术</category><category>人类学</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Top Turkish Diplomat Slams Kilicdaroglu Over Russia Meddling Claims]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110507827" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/04/08/1082575438_0:0:2923:2047_1440x900_80_0_1_da68dac85eb6b172d315c0667409c5e4.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1082575436" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/top-turkish-diplomat-slams-kilicdaroglu-over-russia-meddling-claims-1110507827.html?share-img=1082575436"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / Stephanie Lecocq</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">2021 年 1 月 21 日，星期四，土耳其外交部长梅夫卢特·恰武什奥卢 (Mevlut Cavusoglu) 与欧盟外交政策负责人何塞普·博雷尔 (Josep Borrell) 在布鲁塞尔举行会议之前发表联合声明。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="Turkey's Foreign Minister Mevlut Cavusoglu gives a joint statement with European Union foreign policy chief Josep Borrell prior to their meeting in Brussels, Thursday, Jan. 21, 2021. - Sputnik International, 1920, 21.05.2023" title="2021 年 1 月 21 日，星期四，土耳其外交部长梅夫鲁特·恰武什奥卢 (Mevlut Cavusoglu) 与欧盟外交政策负责人何塞普·博雷尔 (Josep Borrell) 在布鲁塞尔举行会议之前发表了联合声明。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/04/08/1082575438_0:202:2923:1846_1920x0_80_0_0_46fb3cd89a60a40bb8ab91a37d8aa117.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/04/08/1082575438_0:202:2923:1846_640x0_80_0_0_6c844926341aec0f3b46944280225b79.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/04/08/1082575438_0:202:2923:1846_1280x0_80_0_0_eae1adc5a4e1214b26ab9e96fa12b2b9.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/04/08/1082575438_0:202:2923:1846_1920x0_80_0_0_46fb3cd89a60a40bb8ab91a37d8aa117.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 美联社照片 / Stephanie Lecocq </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据安卡拉（人造卫星）网报道：土耳其外交部长梅夫鲁特·恰武什奥卢批评反对派领导人凯末尔·基利奇达罗格鲁错误地指责俄罗斯干预将于下周日决定的总统竞选。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> Kilicdaroglu 在第一轮投票前表示，俄罗斯正在干涉选举进程，但没有提供任何证据或细节来支持他的说法。克里姆林宫否认了这一指控。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “Kilicdaroglu 先生一直在威胁俄罗斯。破坏我们与这样一个国家的关系是错误的，”Cavusoglu 在接受 Haberturk 新闻频道采访时说。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text">这位部长说，他已经问过将在 5 月 28 日的决选中挑战总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安的 Kilicdaroglu，他是否有任何俄罗斯干预的证据，对此他的回答是“这是我的印象”。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110507827" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/top-turkish-diplomat-slams-kilicdaroglu-over-russia-meddling-claims-1110507827.html?share-block=1110507830" data-title="The minister said he had asked Kilicdaroglu, who will challenge President Recep Tayyip Erdogan in the May 28 runoff, if he had any evidence of Russian meddling, to which he responded with &quot;It was my impression.&quot; "></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>恰武什奥卢表示，这位有抱负的总统应该“更加严肃”，不要根据自己的直觉对其他国家进行无端指责。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这位外交官还否认俄罗斯允许土耳其将天然气付款推迟到 2024 年的决定与选举有任何关系。 Cavusoglu 表示，在去年价格飙升后，Turkiye 正在与所有供应商协商延期支付天然气费用。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">关于叙利亚，恰武什奥卢说，土耳其正在与叙利亚政府谈判难民返回问题。他估计有 50 万叙利亚人从土耳其返回到他们祖国所谓的安全区。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 21 May 2023 22:46:29 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/top-turkish-diplomat-slams-kilicdaroglu-over-russia-meddling-claims-1110507827.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/top-turkish-diplomat-slams-kilicdaroglu-over-russia-meddling-claims-1110507827.html<category>世界</category><category>2023 年土耳其总统选举</category><category>突厥耶</category><category>俄罗斯之门</category><category>俄罗斯</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Bulgarian Protesters Throw Red Paint at EU Liaison Office in Sofia]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110507708" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/104495/39/1044953953_0:0:2048:1369_1440x900_80_0_1_70efa9a14d40b5fe566b2772cbe631da.jpg?source-sid=flickr" data-photoview-image-id="1044953952" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/bulgarian-protesters-throw-red-paint-at-eu-liaison-office-in-sofia-1110507708.html?share-img=1044953952"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Flickr / <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/farmking/3649465749/" title="亚历克斯·洛弗尔-特洛伊">Alex Lovell-Troy</a></span><span class="photoview__desc-text">保加利亚国旗</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="flickr" alt="Bulgarian flag - Sputnik International, 1920, 21.05.2023" title="保加利亚国旗" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/104495/39/1044953953_0:0:2049:1153_1920x0_80_0_0_5ea732e0f93cd4fef711d236c37eef4c.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/104495/39/1044953953_0:0:2049:1153_640x0_80_0_0_d0c10887cc1938014b3df01a0c452777.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/104495/39/1044953953_0:0:2049:1153_1280x0_80_0_0_4e909a020b934da8aabeec4f75aa48d3.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/104495/39/1044953953_0:0:2049:1153_1920x0_80_0_0_5ea732e0f93cd4fef711d236c37eef4c.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Flickr / <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/farmking/3649465749/" title="亚历克斯·洛弗尔-特洛伊">Alex Lovell-Troy</a> </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据莫斯科（人造卫星）网报道：周日，保加利亚抗议者用红色油漆涂抹了欧盟驻索非亚联络处的入口，以抗议其干涉东欧国家的内政。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">来自右翼 Vazrazhdane（复兴）党的集会组织者发布了一段视频，视频显示一大群人在欧盟代表团的正面投掷装满红漆的气球。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">示威者挥舞着保加利亚国旗和标语牌，上面写着“布鲁塞尔之上的保加利亚宪法”和“北约出局！保加利亚是一个和平区”。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="social"><div class="ria-tweet"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">不能接受！！！今天，这发生在<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Bulgaria?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Bulgaria</a>索非亚的欧洲议会大楼。<br>我希望保加利亚当局进行调查，将违法者绳之以法。 <a href="https://twitter.com/Europarl_EN?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Europarl_EN</a> <a href="https://t.co/xc2NCapo3X">pic.twitter.com/xc2NCapo3X</a></p> - Estefanía Meléndez (@EstefaniaVenBg) <a href="https://twitter.com/EstefaniaVenBg/status/1660328670542610437?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 5 月 21 日</a></blockquote></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">据保加利亚通讯社 BTA 报道，索非亚市中心街道的交通中断了半小时，该地区的警力有所增加。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 21 May 2023 21:50:25 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/bulgarian-protesters-throw-red-paint-at-eu-liaison-office-in-sofia-1110507708.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/bulgarian-protesters-throw-red-paint-at-eu-liaison-office-in-sofia-1110507708.html<category>俄罗斯在乌克兰的特别行动</category><category>保加利亚</category><category>反对</category><category>政治抗议</category><category>乌克兰</category><category>乌克兰危机</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Greek Opposition Leader Concedes Defeat to New Democracy Party's Victory in Parliamentary Polls]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110507585" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/06/15/1096518605_0:0:3072:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_dc84576af89082c1b3673469451c4d82.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1096518588" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/greek-opposition-leader-concedes-defeat-to-new-democracy-partys-victory-in-parliamentary-polls-1110507585.html?share-img=1096518588"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / Geert Vanden Wijngaert</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">2022 年 5 月 30 日，星期一，希腊总理 Kyriakos Mitsotakis 在布鲁塞尔欧罗巴大楼举行的欧盟领导人特别会议讨论乌克兰、能源和粮食安全之前向媒体发表讲话</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="Greek Prime Minister Kyriakos Mitsotakis speaks to media prior the extraordinary meeting of EU leaders to discuss Ukraine, energy and food security at the Europa building in Brussels, Monday, May 30, 2022 - Sputnik International, 1920, 21.05.2023" title="2022 年 5 月 30 日，星期一，希腊总理基里亚科斯·米佐塔基斯在布鲁塞尔欧罗巴大楼举行的欧盟领导人特别会议讨论乌克兰、能源和粮食安全之前向媒体发表讲话" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/06/15/1096518605_0:125:3072:1853_1920x0_80_0_0_8a22eb8af99255cea34a695cf81e9533.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/06/15/1096518605_0:125:3072:1853_640x0_80_0_0_1aa13a3258e34d01be5d29c8d0ae491f.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/06/15/1096518605_0:125:3072:1853_1280x0_80_0_0_ee359bad0d29426b6dc7756c4e61ee85.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/06/15/1096518605_0:125:3072:1853_1920x0_80_0_0_8a22eb8af99255cea34a695cf81e9533.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 美联社照片 / Geert Vanden Wijngaert </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据雅典（人造卫星）网报道：据官方媒体报道，希腊反对党领袖亚历克西斯·齐普拉斯祝贺总理基里亚科斯·米佐塔基斯新民主党在周日的议会选举中获胜。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">内政部公布的结果显示，右翼新民主党在齐普拉斯的左翼激进左翼联盟党中遥遥领先。投票率超过60%。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text">在超过 90% 的选票被清点后，执政党将在 300 个席位的议会中获得 40.81% 的选票和 146 个席位，而左翼激进联盟党将获得 20.06% 的选票和 71 个席位。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110507585" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/greek-opposition-leader-concedes-defeat-to-new-democracy-partys-victory-in-parliamentary-polls-1110507585.html?share-block=1110507587" data-title="After more than 90% of ballots were counted, the ruling party stood to gain 40.81% of the vote and 146 seats in the 300-seat parliament, against Syriza’s 20.06% of the vote and 71 seats. "></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">中左翼泛希社工党以 11.58% 和 41 个席位位居第三，其次是共产党以 7.18% 和 26 个席位，以及极右翼希腊解决方案以 4.46% 和 16 个席位。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">由于没有绝对多数，预计稍后将再次进行议会投票。国有 ERT 新闻频道称，前总理齐普拉斯致电米佐塔基斯提议将 6 月 25 日或 7 月 2 日作为下一次投票的暂定日期。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>米佐塔基斯称投票结果是“巨大而明显的胜利”。他说，他认为这一结果是对他的路线的认可，也是新民主党单独执政的明确授权，暗示他将在下一次投票中寻求绝对多数。</strong></div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 21 May 2023 21:16:05 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/greek-opposition-leader-concedes-defeat-to-new-democracy-partys-victory-in-parliamentary-polls-1110507585.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/greek-opposition-leader-concedes-defeat-to-new-democracy-partys-victory-in-parliamentary-polls-1110507585.html<category>世界</category><category>希腊</category><category>希腊新民主党</category><category>投票</category><category>世界政治</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[UK Military Attributes Success of Russian Strikes Deep Into Ukraine to Improved Use of Spy Drones]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110507133" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110507298_0:0:1416:784_1440x900_80_0_1_3e03dad34458530ca8fdb15136a1566f.png?source-sid=not_sputnik_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1110507280" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/uk-military-attributes-success-of-russian-strikes-deep-into-ukraine-to-improved-use-of-spy-drones-1110507133.html?share-img=1110507280"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© 照片：YouTube / Supercam UAV</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">Supercam SX350 间谍无人机在测试期间。公司视频截图。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="not_sputnik_photo" alt="a Supercam SX350 spy drone during testing. Screengrab of company video. - Sputnik International, 1920, 21.05.2023" title="测试期间的 Supercam SX350 间谍无人机。公司视频截图。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110507298_12:0:1406:784_1920x0_80_0_0_14fdf8d9ac1f1040f0426b9135077ba7.png" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110507298_12:0:1406:784_640x0_80_0_0_63337d4601f7cb553cc957bd67243850.png 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110507298_12:0:1406:784_1280x0_80_0_0_72ea7f5799addd9fcf6438a6b41e52cb.png 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110507298_12:0:1406:784_1920x0_80_0_0_14fdf8d9ac1f1040f0426b9135077ba7.png 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 照片：YouTube / Supercam UAV </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">伊利亚楚卡诺夫</div><div class="article__author-links"> <a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_tsukanov_ilya/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:i.tsukanov@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">最近几周，俄罗斯军方大幅加强了对乌克兰前线深处目标的空袭和导弹打击，使用无人机和导弹（包括 Kh-47M2 Kinzhal）瞄准部队、装甲、弹药库和防空系统。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">英国国防部将整个 5 月份“频繁的 [俄罗斯] 远程导弹深入乌克兰”的成功归因于俄罗斯军方改进了“非武装、监视型非螺旋式飞行器 (UAV) 与行动的结合”。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “这些包括俄罗斯生产的 Supercam 无人机，它们相对便宜并且有足够的射程飞越巡航导弹的目标，”国防部在周日的国防情报更新中<a href="https://twitter.com/DefenceHQ/status/1660161473455218688" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">说</a>。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110507133" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/uk-military-attributes-success-of-russian-strikes-deep-into-ukraine-to-improved-use-of-spy-drones-1110507133.html?share-block=1110507135" data-title="“These have included Russian-produced Supercam UAVs which are relatively cheap and have sufficient range to fly over the cruise missiles’ targets,” the MoD said in a defense intelligence update Sunday."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">军方表示：“俄罗斯极有可能采用这种战术，以试图获得更及时的战斗损害评估并改善其瞄准周期，”并指出俄罗斯军队之前“缓慢而低效的瞄准过程”已被证明是一个“主要弱点”在乌克兰开展业务。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> Supercam Unmanned Systems Group 是俄罗斯主要的无人机生产商，为军用和民用市场生产无人机。这种由螺旋桨驱动的小型无人机的飞行距离在 50 至 450 公里之间，无线电链路范围可达 110 公里，翼展范围为 1 至 4.5 米，续航时间长达 7 小时。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 21 May 2023 18:58:55 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/uk-military-attributes-success-of-russian-strikes-deep-into-ukraine-to-improved-use-of-spy-drones-1110507133.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/uk-military-attributes-success-of-russian-strikes-deep-into-ukraine-to-improved-use-of-spy-drones-1110507133.html<category>俄罗斯在乌克兰的特别行动</category><category>乌克兰</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>英国</category><category>无人机</category><category>无人机战争</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Russia Would Ruin F-16’s Reputation by Destroying Jets Sent to Kiev]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110506754" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/13/1110456552_0:0:2000:977_1440x900_80_0_1_d69bae7ef171fc7f43b5e273e5a04964.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1110456534" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/russia-would-ruin-f-16s-reputation-by-destroying-jets-sent-to-kiev-1110506754.html?share-img=1110456534"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / Toby Talbot</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">在这张 2001 年 12 月的档案照片中，一架 F-16 从佛蒙特州南伯灵顿的空军国民警卫队基地起飞，加力燃烧室发光，满载响尾蛇导弹。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="In this Dec. 2001 file photograph, an F-16 takes off with afterburners glowing loaded with live Sidewinder missiles from the Air National Guard base in South Burlington, Vt. - Sputnik International, 1920, 21.05.2023" title="在这张 2001 年 12 月的档案照片中，一架 F-16 从佛蒙特州南伯灵顿的空军国民警卫队基地起飞，加力燃烧室发光，满载响尾蛇导弹。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/13/1110456552_132:0:1869:977_1920x0_80_0_0_baddefe375461e4835f816ccca217a9d.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/13/1110456552_132:0:1869:977_640x0_80_0_0_dff1a8ee0288d3203705432fcd4a1f9a.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/13/1110456552_132:0:1869:977_1280x0_80_0_0_d2342fbe5579328e15a2778f9527c8c9.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/13/1110456552_132:0:1869:977_1920x0_80_0_0_baddefe375461e4835f816ccca217a9d.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 美联社照片 / Toby Talbot </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">伊利亚楚卡诺夫</div><div class="article__author-links"> <a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_tsukanov_ilya/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:i.tsukanov@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">在华盛顿批准培训乌克兰飞行员驾驶飞机后，基辅希望从其北约“伙伴”那里接收数十架 F-16 战斗机。莫斯科发誓要将 F-16 的部署纳入其军事战略，并警告说这种“升级情景”会给西方带来“巨大风险”。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> F-16——美国的主力第四代多用途战斗机，如果飞机被送往乌克兰并在其机场被摧毁或在空战中被俄罗斯喷气式飞机击落，其声誉将受到严重打击。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这是根据一家独立军事新闻门户网站的<a href="https://militarywatchmagazine.com/article/us-reluctant-f16s-ukraine-euro-pressure" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">最新分析得出</a>的，该门户网站援引华盛顿此前表示不愿让荷兰和挪威等盟国向乌克兰提供老式 F-16 战机的迹象表明，美国官员承认“美国将承担主要风险”。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “不仅战斗机或其技术有可能落入俄罗斯手中，因为其他西方装备数量相当可观，而且战斗机在机场和飞机上的袭击中遭受重大损失的可能性也更大。在空战中，这将对 F-16 的声誉造成重大打击，”该门户网站指出。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110506754" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/russia-would-ruin-f-16s-reputation-by-destroying-jets-sent-to-kiev-1110506754.html?share-block=1110506757" data-title="“Not only is there a possibility that the fighter or its technologies could fall into Russian hands, as other Western equipment has in considerable quantities, but there is also a much greater chance that the fighters could suffer significant losses both to strikes on their airfields and in air-to-air combat which would be a major blow to the F-16’s reputation,” the portal noted."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">指出 F-16 与同行竞争者的地位越来越过时，该媒体强调，在与俄罗斯空中力量的战斗中，“由于缺乏隐身能力和与俄罗斯机队高端重型飞机交战的能力有限”，包括 Su-35、MiG-31 和 Su-57。部署到乌克兰也意味着容易受到俄罗斯远程地对空导弹的攻击。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">该门户网站指出，继周二俄罗斯金扎尔<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/what-is-the-fastest-missile-in-the-world-and-how-much-does-speed-really-matter-1110502411.html" target="_blank">高超音速导弹</a><a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/kinzhal-missile-strike-destroyed-five-patriot-launchers-in-kiev---russia-1110424974.html" target="_blank">成功攻击</a>爱国者导弹防御系统后，美国军工联合体本周已经遭受重大声誉打击。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">分析指出，虽然升级后的 Block 70/72 F-16 可能“有潜力”对抗俄罗斯的战斗机，但这种飞机的制造量还不到两打，而且它们每架 1.2 亿美元以上的成本可能使它们的部署成本高得令人望而却步到乌克兰，洛克希德·马丁公司更愿意将它们卖给亚洲和中东的买家。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">该媒体的担忧呼应了前美国空军飞行员转为传统基金会研究员约翰维纳布尔的担忧，他<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230505/us-f-16s-in-ukraine-would-be-completely-outmatched-by-russias-s-400-air-defense-1110109419.html" target="_blank">本月早些时候警告说，</a> F-16 在乌克兰这样的高威胁环境中将“完全无法匹敌”，而俄罗斯的 S- 400 个防空系统将能够在喷气式飞机有机会接近到足以发动攻击之前锁定它们。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">拜登总统周日承认，F-16 的部署“根本不会帮助”基辅保卫最近失守的顿涅茨克市阿尔捷莫夫斯克（巴赫穆特） <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/biden-says-default-on-debt-not-an-option-congress-leaders-must-live-up-to-commitments-1110500068.html" target="_blank">。</a>星期四，美国总统<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230520/biden-oks-training-ukrainians-on-f-16s-but-timeline-remains-uncertain-1110474001.html" target="_blank">通知</a>他的七国集团同行，华盛顿将支持共同努力训练乌克兰飞行员操作第四代喷气式飞机，包括 F-16。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text">白宫国家安全顾问杰克沙利文<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230520/biden-oks-training-ukrainians-on-f-16s-but-timeline-remains-uncertain-1110474001.html" target="_blank">拒绝</a>提供有关此次培训的任何细节或时间表，也拒绝透露喷气式飞机何时可以运抵基辅。 “我们的观点是，F-16 适合战斗的地方现在还不合适。因此，如果我们现在拥有它，那么这不是他们在战场上进行反攻所需的主要重点。所以我们觉得我们将能够在他们需要的时候为他们提供未来部队所需的东西，”沙利文周六<a href="https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/press-briefings/2023/05/20/press-briefing-by-press-secretary-karine-jean-pierre-and-national-security-advisor-jake-sullivan-on-the-presidents-trip-to-japan/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">告诉记者</a>。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110506754" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/russia-would-ruin-f-16s-reputation-by-destroying-jets-sent-to-kiev-1110506754.html?share-block=1110506763" data-title="White House national security advisor Jake Sullivan declined to offer any details or a timetable on this training, or when jets could be delivered to Kiev. “Our view is that where the F-16 fits into the fight is not right now. So if we had it right now, this is not the main focus of what they need on the battlefield for this counteroffensive. So we feel like we will be in a position to give them what they need for that future force when they need it,” Sullivan told reporters Saturday."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">多个美国盟友<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/poland-handed-over-all-of-its-mig-29-fighters-to-ukraine---president-1110415874.html" target="_blank">表示</a>，他们不准备将 F-16 供应给乌克兰。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">四十多年来，F-16 的变种一直是美国空军和其他两个国家空军的骨干力量，并被广泛用作美国和北约在伊拉克、南斯拉夫、阿富汗和利比亚，以及涉及以色列、巴基斯坦、海湾国家、摩洛哥和约旦的冲突。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 21 May 2023 18:45:12 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/russia-would-ruin-f-16s-reputation-by-destroying-jets-sent-to-kiev-1110506754.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/russia-would-ruin-f-16s-reputation-by-destroying-jets-sent-to-kiev-1110506754.html<category>世界</category><category>杰克沙利文</category><category>乔·拜登</category><category>乌克兰</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>北约</category><category>歼16</category><category>战斗机</category><category>送货</category><category>洛克希德马丁公司</category></item></channel></rss>